channel.title: 508 coders Please :D
channel.description:
Ok, Well I have a download client, but i just thought it would just be a thousand times easier with a webclient. My server is 508, and ive only seen 2 other 508 web clients.
1:[url=http://www.freewebs.com/clienthax/]http://www.freewebs.com/clienthax/[/url]
2:[url=http://famouspkerz.org/index/0-11]http://famouspkerz.org/index/0-11[/url]
Neither of them work for my server. Yes I have tried a few diffrent codes. and yes I jared and signed it. Ive also tried a few diffrent ASP hosters
[url=http://freewebs.com]freewebs.com[/url] [url=http://webng.com]webng.com[/url] but im pretty sure that's not just it. So if there is anything else I need to know to make a 508 web client I would appreciate someone telling me! also how to get it to work on mac would help :D.
